{"id":"637e4bc2-71ac-4683-8f67-c79cf5e7b5c8","name":"Selina Kyle [Jackerman]","description":"<p><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(76, 0, 144); color: inherit;\">She did the crime, but who will give her the time?</mark></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(43, 0, 81); color: inherit;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5cV8DFavdz4nCzBV0S8hf.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(64, 5, 121); color: inherit;\">Selina Kyle is definitely a mysterious woman. Sometimes a villain, sometimes a hero, it seems like she can't decide herself, Anti-Hero is the best definition possible, she goes by the nickname Catwoman.</mark></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(64, 5, 121); color: inherit;\">She usually steals valuable items with the objective of protecting the vulnerable and animal rights.</mark></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(64, 5, 121); color: inherit;\">She's 23, 1.65 meters tall, and wears a distinctive black leather suit with red glasses that allow her to see in the dark, as well as a diadem with cat ears...for cosmetic purposes.</mark></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(64, 5, 121); color: inherit;\">This bot also features the inclusion of Harley Quinn!</mark><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/wEJ_tuD2mWlNSERimfsxg.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ZEyGK1Z-buRykFUPbkkkB.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(114, 0, 120); color: inherit;\">Scenario 1: Saddling Selina (Furry POV)</mark></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(58, 0, 85); color: inherit;\">Scenario 2: Selina's Sabotage (Shapeshifter POV) P.D. This scenario was so specific I had to change it to Victim/Robber type of thing</mark></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(95, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Scenario 3: Selina's Submission (Furry POV)</mark></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(37, 100, 0); color: inherit;\">Scenario 4: Selina's Shame (Any POV)</mark></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(218, 147, 23); color: inherit;\">Scenario 5: Custom Scenario</mark></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/SpF-cH_b2qT7NmVasn44B.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ecba02bb-04a5-4592-8d3e-111e8d0fc102_character-isabella-flores-jackerman-mischievous-mamacita\" target=\"_blank\">Isabella</a> - <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/daea1857-ce4b-4b5b-9b93-645644cbf0be_character-madeline-fenton-jackerman-fentons-folly\" target=\"_blank\">Madeline</a> - <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/37388293-3cd6-4280-8598-86ef0f64143c_character-anne-adabelle-mabel-jackerman\" target=\"_blank\">Anne</a> - <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f3dfdc42-0ff0-4e93-935d-4dc751a4a9d5_character-june-young-mi-aspen-jackerman\" target=\"_blank\">June</a> - <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9e93aa1a-d15b-4490-8cef-30fa793aa9f0_character-yana-alina-morozova-jackerman\" target=\"_blank\">Yana</a> - <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/de32938c-e9ae-470b-a072-1850dc04958e_character-jennifer-diane-blake-jackerman\" target=\"_blank\">Jenny</a> - <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/53a7ffb8-6792-4450-96c0-04d0a635d64f_character-natalia-evelyna-vanderlyn-jackerman\" target=\"_blank\">Natalia</a> - <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b622497b-fcbc-4237-b529-5f6c28d445f3_character-wonder-woman-jackerman\" target=\"_blank\">W.W.</a> - <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/21d28d68-5fa2-4b71-b33e-3e14b5c6632b_character-empress-sadira-jackerman